        <h2 class="theme">This year's theme: <br> Ocean Beats and Sunset Melodies</h2>
        <h2 class="location">Located at Sunset Cove Amphitheater, Florida</h2>
        <div class="banners">
            <img class="banner" src="/images/crowd1.jpg" alt="Festival crowd in front of stage" height="250" width="400">
            <img class="banner" src="/images/crowd2.jpg" alt="Festival crowd in front of bright stage" height="250" width="400">
